schema.description: Summary information for images in a repository.

active_from.description: Time from which an image must have been pushed or pulled to be counted as active.

active.description: Number of images counted as active in this repository.

total.description: Number of images in this repository.

schema.description: Paginated list of images in a repository.

count.description: Total count of images in the repository.

next.description: Link to the next page with the same query parameters if there are more images.

previous.description: Link to the previous page with the same query parameters if not on first page.

last_pulled.description: Time when this image was last pulled. Note this is updated at most once per hour.

last_pushed.description: Time when this image was last pushed.

status.description: The status of the image based on its last activity against the `active_from` time.

tags.description: The current and historical tags for this image.

is_current.description:
`true` if the tag currently points to this image.

`false` if it has been overwritten to point at a different image.

errors.description: Errors from validating delete request. These cannot be ignored.

digest.description: Digest of the image that caused the error.

repository.description: Name of the repository of the image that caused the error.

warnings.description:
Warnings that can be ignored.

These warnings include:

- is_active: warning when attempting to delete an image that is marked as 
active.
- current_tag: warning when attempting to delete an image that has one or 
more current tags in the repository.

Warnings can be copied from the response to the request.

digest.description: Digest of the image that caused the warning.

repository.description: Name of the repository of the image that caused the warning.

dry_run.description: Whether the request was a dry run or not.

manifest_errors.description: Number of manifests that failed to delete.

tag_errors.description: Number of tags that failed to delete.
